Module ru.nsu.plodushcheva
Package ru.nsu.plodushcheva.model.json

Class JsonData

java.lang.Object
ru.nsu.plodushcheva.model.json.JsonData
public class JsonData extends Object
The JsonData class represents the JSON data used for configuring the game. It contains various properties such as width, height, food settings, and wall positions for different levels.

  • Constructor Details

    • JsonData

      public JsonData​(int width, int height, int columns, int rows, int squareSize, int maxFoodForLevel1, int maxFoodForLevel2, int maxFoodForLevel3, int speedFoodForLevel1, int speedFoodForLevel2, int speedFoodForLevel3, List<Point> wallsFoodForLevel1, List<Point> wallsFoodForLevel2, List<Point> wallsFoodForLevel3)
      Represents the JSON data used in the game.
      Parameters:
      width - The width of the game field.
      height - The height of the game field.
      columns - The number of columns in the game field.
      rows - The number of rows in the game field.
      squareSize - The size of each square in the game field.
      maxFoodForLevel1 - The maximum number of food for level 1.
      maxFoodForLevel2 - The maximum number of food for level 2.
      maxFoodForLevel3 - The maximum number of food for level 3.
      speedFoodForLevel1 - The speed of food for level 1.
      speedFoodForLevel2 - The speed of food for level 2.
      speedFoodForLevel3 - The speed of food for level 3.
      wallsFoodForLevel1 - The list of wall coordinates for level 1.
      wallsFoodForLevel2 - The list of wall coordinates for level 2.
      wallsFoodForLevel3 - The list of wall coordinates for level 3.
